Author: Poonam Sharma Dronamraju
Content:
Propolis especially the one Vimergy makes has extraordinary power, whenever my toothbrush causes a cankersore I apply it and the sore is gone within a day. Also implies it was time for me to change brush heads. Eternally grateful to SOC and AW for sharing this information, thank you so much. Many Blessings 🙏🏾♥️♾️♥️🌺

I used it during the plague of 2020. Propolis every 3 hours in my throat healed with 4 days

Author: Maria Ermo
Content: Medical Medium vimergy suplements are very goog but It is difficult to access them from the European market as they are expensive and with the shipping costs (especially now) it is almost an impossible task. My question is whether you intend to create a European market with them??

Author: Kelly Atwell
Content: That’s great to know! I had a similar experience with olive leaf. I was suffering with a cold, flu, covid not sure which one but very sick. I took a dropper full of olive Leaf and the instant it hit my throat I had relief and was able to sleep with no sore throat.
